my AWS account and if there are resources outside of the AWS account,

00:01:11.130 --> 00:01:14.510
this gives you the opportunity to have these boundaries where you can have

00:01:14.510 --> 00:01:19.325
this line specifying what's inside and what's outside.

00:01:19.325 --> 00:01:25.915
One example that I could give you right now is I can click search here and type users,

00:01:25.915 --> 00:01:30.590
and you will have users here and I'm going to drag this over here,

00:01:30.590 --> 00:01:33.485
and I'm going to change the text,

00:01:33.485 --> 00:01:37.920
