00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:42.710
What this means is if you have a web application that you're running,

00:01:42.710 --> 00:01:45.560
the users means the web visitors

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:48.650
and those are going to be obviously outside of your cloud,

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:51.810
they just come from the internet in this case.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:57.700
